<p><em>A beautiful wine from a near-perfect vintage, this robust Cabernet Sauvignon shows balance and complexity - a blend of dark berry, generous oak notes, clove, and nutmeg. This is a supple and complex, full-bodied in style, with a punch of power, ripeness, and elegance from start to finish.</em></p>
