<h3 id="region">Region</h3>
<p><strong>Napa Valley, California</strong>
Sourced primarily from our family owned S&amp;J Vineyard in Napa‚Äôs Capell Valley and our Benjamin Vineyard located on the valley floor in the heart of Rutherford. Additional vineyard sources include neighboring Quarry Vineyard and Round Pond Estate both in Rutherford as well as Delouise and Shooting Star Vineyard located in Napa Valley.</p>

<h3 id="winemaking">Winemaking</h3>
<p><strong>Winemaker Notes</strong> ‚Üí Our goal is to make a complete, balanced wine. Cabernet Sauvignon is a great grape, it‚Äôs the king of Napa Valley after all. But it can benefit from the addition of other grapes, like Merlot which adds some softness. Together you get the whole package.</p>

